<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <!-- 1. WhatsApp reads these tags first -->
    <meta property="og:title" content="STEMSync" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Interactive demos with live syncing" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://example.com" />

    <!-- 2. Instant browser redirect fallback -->
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0; url=https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbzJdc-POuVRm5rXY1193YRRMqAAedjl-RaLEcKe2QZH_IarcbWV0jkR7mJlX39DBZpj/exec?webrtc=true&role=guest" />
    
    <!-- 3. Immediate JavaScript redirect (in case the browser blocks meta refresh) -->
    <script>
        window.location.href = "https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbzJdc-POuVRm5rXY1193YRRMqAAedjl-RaLEcKe2QZH_IarcbWV0jkR7mJlX39DBZpj/exec?webrtc=true&role=guest";
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Redirecting you to the app... If you are not redirected, <a href="https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbzJdc-POuVRm5rXY1193YRRMqAAedjl-RaLEcKe2QZH_IarcbWV0jkR7mJlX39DBZpj/exec?webrtc=true&role=guest">click here</a>.</p>
</body>
</html>
